The way that this works for sign up:
(Client Calculates Salt & Hash from password)
1. Client Posts username, salt, hash
2. We store username, salt, hash

For Sign In:
1. Client Gets salt & hash with username
2. Server Gives Salt
(Client Calculates Hash from password & Salt)
3. Client Sends back Salt & Username
4. Server Calculates & Stores Session ID In RAM
5. Server Sends Back Session ID
